@node sect2 "Description"
This manual page documents briefly the @{b}tint@{ub} clone. As with all games (and especially with tint), you have to play it, not read about it. 
@endnode

@node sect3 "Options"
A summary of options is included below. For a complete description, see the NOTES file in /usr/share/doc/tint. 

· @{b}-h@{ub} @{lindent 3}
Show summary of options. @{lindent 0}

· @{b}-l <level>@{ub} @{lindent 3}
Specify the starting level (1-9). The higher the level you're starting from, the faster you'll earn points. @{lindent 0}

· @{b}-n@{ub} @{lindent 3}
Draw next shape. When the next shape is drawn, you might find the game to be easier, but it will be slower to earn points. @{lindent 0}


